**A REALM IS ENTERED:**

What is your name?

>> Dan Farrer

Welcome to the Realm, Dan Farrer.

This is your first time here. Don't be scared. Don't be nervous. Don't be confused by the twisty little passages, all alike[0]. There aren't any[1]. Don't look around too fast; our profile on you indicates that your graphical capabilities are not sufficient to render a requisite number of polygons. VeraGames extends its apologies. Don't stray into the water - you can't swim, yet[2]. Don't be worried about visual artifacts. Don't spend too long here; be sure to surface occasionally for food and sunshine[3]. Don't be caught unaware, because death in the Realm will require you to start again.

>>[10] _If only they could tell me what I_ could _do. All these don'ts are boggling my mind._

Don't be off-put by the number of "don't"s. 

>> _Thanks._

Don't not be welcomed.

>> _That's a double negative._

Don't be alarmed of double negatives.

>> _Is this game reading my mind?_

Don't--

...

Kind of.

>> _Kind of? Does that mean you have access to all my deep secrets and desires? Like that one time c- actually, forget that._

Forgotten.

>> _But do answer my question._

What question?

>> _Bah, nevermind. Look around._

It is the year 2044, the eighth year of the Realm. You find yourself in a quaint HOME. At least presumably. You are standing next to your BED, as if you have just woken up, perhaps for the first time. You sense some METAPHORICAL SIGNIFICANCE of this fact. The SUN filters in through your FENESTRATIONS. There is a NOTE on your dresser.

What do you do?

>> _How can I talk to my friends in this thing?_

That's not something you can do.

>> _What can I do then?_

That's not something you can do.

